casebody.data:
STEPHENSON
v.
PALMATIER, et al. No. 356P15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Nov. 5, 2015. Terry W. Stephenson, II, Lowell, for Stephenson, Terry Wayne (II). Jeffrey Goss, Attorney at Law, for Palmatier, Terry L., et al. Linda G. Wideman, for Wideman, Linda G.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 26th of October 2015 by Plaintiff for Petition for Preliminary Injunction:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of November 2015."
